 discovery;\npost-gen-interventions/com.sun.xml.bind_jaxb-impl_2.2.3-1.md:30:- reflection access for JAXB DOM handling such as `javax.xml.bind.annotation.W3CDomHandler.<init>()` when `@XmlAnyElement` is exercised.\npost-gen-interventions/com.sun.xml.bind_jaxb-impl_2.2.3-1.md:32:The Codex metadata-fix log shows Codex was still in an iterative metadata-repair loop. It added several candidate metadata entries and then planned another pinned-GraalVM verification run, but the log ends immediately after JSON validation with a recorder error: `No space left on device (os error 28)`. Codex therefore did not complete a successful verify cycle and did not prove that the final metadata set was sufficient.\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.sun.xml.bind:jaxb-impl:2.2.3-1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T10-20-25-712100Z.log:321:>     => org.graalvm.nativeimage.MissingReflectionRegistrationError: Cannot reflectively access the proxy class inheriting ['com.sun.xml.bind.v2.schemagen.xmlschema.Schema'].\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.sun.xml.bind:jaxb-impl:2.2.3-1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T10-20-25-712100Z.log:339:BUILD FAILED in 53s\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.sun.xml.bind:jaxb-impl:2.2.3-1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T10-20-25-712100Z.log:401:BUILD FAILED in 55s\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.sun.xml.bind:jaxb-impl:2.2.3-1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T10-02-34-346947Z.log:306:    => org.graalvm.nativeimage.MissingReflectionRegistrationError: Cannot reflectively invoke method 'public static javax.xml.bind.JAXBContext com.sun.xml.bind.v2.ContextFactory.createContext(java.lang.Class[],java.util.Map) throws javax.xml.bind.JAXBException'.\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.sun.xml.bind:jaxb-impl:2.2.3-1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T10-02-34-346947Z.log:311:      \"type\": \"com.sun.xml.bind.v2.ContextFactory\",\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.sun.xml.bind:jaxb-impl:2.2.3-1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-09T10-02-34-346947Z.log:314:          \"name\": \"createContext\",\nhu